|    Note   | `#nte-` | [style="color: blue;" ]{.nte} | Book differences / H0-HA          |
|    Tip    | `#tip-` | [style="color: darkgreen;"]{.tip}   | Learning reminder / Report  |
|  Caution  | `#cau-` | [style="color: darkgoldenrod;"]{.cau} | Pay attention             |
